b8c8b5ca9f79b79ad78636bf4e3d36864c26b64a618a810a76ed0c026f9b530bfba3561269cadd9e54ee3ba47bc02c8bac18ffbd1cd25037bfdee25a081fc125  0001-pcre2-riscv64-support.patch"
